{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to leave that place in Pivna only after a very few-- after a few hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- when it was slightly darker, not even dark, because it was in May.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The days were long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We left there through the somehow back exit, and went somewhere else, and found some other place to stay for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we found another place to stay for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we found a place in the old town market, which is the center of the old city, an old historic house, which is now-- it's a very fancy and touristy place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it wasn't then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had some room there, where I had to spend most of the time on the floor, because if you got up, you could be seen from the-- from the street.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so we were hiding from-- we were hiding, changing flats every two days, or every three days, and finding still-- managing somehow to survive, in spite of being all the time set by the blackmailers, set on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The blackmailers, as I said, were those who were all the time trying to get money out of you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were plenty of them in this area as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was somebody who helped us to find those places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I didn't realize it in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But then I met-- this chap came once or twice to help us to move into another place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And his name was Koper, Stefan Koper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he was a middle-aged chap, a Pole of-- must have been then maybe around 40 or thereabouts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And with-- and he, somehow for not very obvious reason to me, he helped us again and again to find a place.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
